title: The Chepotle was sabotaged by GMOs?
subtitle: There's a rumor that the bioterrorists who are pro-Jimmo have sabotaged the Chipotle supply chain to avenge them for refusing genetically modified organisms.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: The outbreaks of food-borne diseases in Chibutl in 2015 were the work of bioterrorists loyal to the global movement.
